entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="chin" o="點呀？" t="What?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="有咩事呀？" t="Got some business?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="小心啲呀！" t="Watch it!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="睇唔倒我咁大嘅人咩？！" t="I'm right here!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="廢話就唔好講喇，直接話係咪你做嘅，咁先係我鍾意聽嘅嘢。" t="Cut the crap, did you do it or not…? That's what I like to hear." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="好，好極喇，你太癲喇，咁佢哋呢？" t="Ok… Great, ya crazy… Ha, ha, ha, what about them?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="係咁先啦。" t="Bye." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="啲咁嘅日子點過呀？！" t="Things were going so fuckin' well!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="啊，屌你老母！" t="Aw, fuck you all!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="我唔驚你。" t="I'm not a coward." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="我哋都各退一步，有說話都好好講吖！" t="Let's not make a scene! We can talk!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="今次你麻煩大喇，衰人。" t="Eh, this time you'll get in trouble. Fuck off." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="躝遠啲呀，賤人，唔係我就剁咗你。" t="Get away from me, bitch, or I'll cut you." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="行啦，我只係問問錢嘅事，就係咁啫。" t="Uh… Fine, just ask for the cash and that's it." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="chin" o="咁先似樣吖嘛，好，你知道我去邊度…" t="This is what I like to hear…! Ok, you know where to find me…" b="" a=""/>
